29/4/2003 YAM 2.4 Released

Latest version of YAM, the popular Email program, is now out. Get it from
http://sourceforge.net/projects/yamos/

YAM (short for 'Yet Another Mailer') is a MIME-compliant Internet mailer 
written for AmigaOS computers. It supports multi-POP3, APOP, SMTP, TLSv1/SSLv3,
 multiple users, PGP, unlimited hierarchical folders, filters, configurable 
GUI, ARexx interface.